<promed@promedmail.org>
[The continuation of FSE in the UK after domestic catfood producers had
removed CNS tissues from the mix was traced to imported catfood from
Europe; see above postings. One must ask why this Swiss cat was diagnosed
correctly and why only one case. And French cats have been exposed,
presumably, and elsewhere. It is of interest that dogs, on much the same
diet, continue to fail to demonstrate a CSE. Maybe they do but never meet a
neuropathologist. - Mod.MHJ
